<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8628272">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8628272/" class="title-link">为宪政鼓与舞</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8628272"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/135340906/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u135340906-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/135340906/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">偉</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2017-06-26"
      class="main-meta">2017-06-26 23:04:06</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8628272_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  本来不想写书评的，看到这么深刻的书，居然没有一篇书评，一定要为蔡定剑和其他一批学者叫好。 人类在民主基础上，建立以宪法为核心的法治，以法治保障人权，限制民主，制约政府权力，这就是宪政 宪政就是民主，法治，人权相互支撑，互相制约的政府，一篇篇学术论文，探索者国...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8628272_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8628272_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评1篇
                </a>
            </p>
